Made this with "flax eggs" (1 tbs ground flax+3 tbs water/egg) and 2% greek yogurt--also used blood orange zest instead of lemon. I also skimped a bit on the sugar and oil. Next time, I may cut the sugar to 3/4 cup (or 1/2 for breakfast). Delicious! Will serve with a blood orange icing. The best part is that I was able to throw it together before heading to work in the morning. This will be a staple!

