Lovely easy cake. I used melted butter and it turned out lovely. Method .... Rub sugar lemon ... Add ugs and yogurt whisk. Stream in butter, vanilla salt, throw in flour and BP... Whisk just till combined... One bowl.. 5 min. Beautiful cake. SO SO SO easy. Could use less butter but why bother. :)

